  <main role="main">

    <div class="container marketing">

      <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7 text-center">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading"><span class="oswald taj_color"> The Apprentice's Journey </span></h2>
          <p class="lead">
                    Every person involved in technology is a recurrent <b class="lead_plus">apprentice</b>.
                                                                                 The apprentice isn't a person or an individual,
                                                                                 it's a set of patterns of behaviors,
                                                                                 habits and experiences about learn, the apprentice is an <b class="lead_plus">arquetype</b>.
                                                                                                                                                    What would happen if we put together the learning archetypes of many persons?
                                                                                                                                                    Maybe we'll find <b class="lead_plus">the apprentice's journey</b>.
          </p>
          <p class="lead_latin">
          <i>
          Cada persona involucrada en tecnología es un <strong class="lead_plus">aprendiz</strong> recurrente.
                                                                      Un aprendiz no es una persona, es el <strong class="lead_plus">conjunto de comportamientos,
                                                                                                                          hábitos y experiencias sobre aprendizaje</strong>. Un aprendiz es más un <strong
                                                                                                                          class="lead_plus">arquetipo</strong>.
                                                                                                                                 ¿Qué pasaría si reunimos los arquetipos de aprendizaje de varias personas?
                                                                                                                                 Quizás encontraremos <strong class="lead_plus">el camino del aprendiz</strong>.
          </i>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5 text-center d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
          <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/carlogilmar/image/upload/v1575604446/apprentices_journey/title_i7wpnr.png" width="80%" alt="Methodology">
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading"><span class="taj_color oswald"> The Interviewees </span></h2>
          <p class="lead">
                    I'm looking for <b class="lead_plus">people</b> involved in technology,
                                              in software development, in Open Source projects, in science, etc,
                                              for have a <b class="lead_plus">conversation</b> about their professions and lifes.
          </p>
          <p class="lead_latin">
          <i>
          Busco personas involucradas en <b class="lead_plus">tecnología</b>, en desarrollo de software,
                                                   en proyectos Open Source, en ciencia, etc, para tener una <b class="lead_plus">conversación</b>
                                                                                                                       acerca de sus profesiones y vidas.
          </i>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 text-center d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
          <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/carlogilmar/image/upload/v1575604446/apprentices_journey/title_i7wpnr.png" width="80%" alt="Methodology">
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-5 text-center">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading"><span class="taj_color oswald"> The Conversation </span></h2>
          <p class="lead">
                    I'm looking for <b class="lead_plus">discover</b> how this people are learning new things,
                                              how they are working in technology, how they are looking for try new technologies,
                                              how they learned about their professions, what kind of books they read, or
                                              what are their main referrences...
          </p>
          <p class="lead_latin">
          <i>
          Busco <b class="lead_plus">descubrir</b> cómo estas personas aprenden nuevas cosas,
                          cómo se relacionan con la tecnología, cómo buscan nuevas tecnologías que probar,
                          cómo aprendieron en su profesión, qué tipo de libros leyeron, o cuáles son
                          sus principales referencias... entre mucho más.
          </i>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-7 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
          <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/carlogilmar/image/upload/v1575604446/apprentices_journey/title_i7wpnr.png" alt="Methodology">
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading"><span class="taj_color"> The Learning Archetype </span></h2>
          <p class="lead">
                    I want to find the behaviors,
                    habits and experiences of <b class="lead_plus">the apprentice</b> that represents the interviewee,
                                                        and thus model their <b class="lead_plus">learning archetype</b>.
          </p>
          <p class="lead_latin">
          <i>
          Quiero encontrar los comportamientos,
          hábitos y experiencias del <b class="lead_plus">aprendiz</b> que representa el entrevistado,
                                               y así modelar su <b class="lead_plus">arquetipo de aprendizaje</b>.
          </i>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-8 text-center d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
          <br><img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/carlogilmar/image/upload/v1575604446/apprentices_journey/title_i7wpnr.png" width="80%" alt="Methodology">
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading"><span class="taj_color"> The Learning System </span></h2>
          <p class="lead">
                    What will we find if we gather many <b class="lead_plus">learning archetypes</b>?
                                                                  Maybe with the right perspective we could find enough patterns
                                                                  that help us to model <b class="lead_plus">the apprentice's journey</b> as a <b>learning system</b>.
          </p>
          <p class="lead_latin">
                    ¿Qué encontraremos si reunimos muchos <b class="lead_plus">arquetipos de aprendizaje</b>?
                                                                    Tal vez con la perspectiva correcta podríamos encontrar suficientes patrones
                                                                    que nos ayuden a modelar <b class="lead_plus">el camino del aprendiz</b> como un sistema de aprendizaje.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 text-center d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
          <br><img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/carlogilmar/image/upload/v1575604446/apprentices_journey/title_i7wpnr.png" width="80%" alt="Methodology">
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <h3 class="text-center"><span class="taj_color oswald"> Suscribe for more information! </span></h3>
      <div class="row featurette text-center">
        <div class="col-md-5"></div>
        <div class="col-md-2 text-center">
          <%= form_for @conn, Routes.signup_path(@conn, :suscribe), [method: :post], fn _f -> %>
            <input type="hidden" name="_csrf_token" id="_csrf_token" value="<%= Plug.CSRFProtection.get_csrf_token() %>" />
            <div class="form-group mb-2">
              <label for="staticEmail2" class="sr-only">Email</label>
              <input required type="text" name="email" class="form-control form-control-sm">
            </div> &nbsp;&nbsp;
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary mb-2 btn_taj"> Suscribe </button>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
